    "description": "<div class=\"stackedit__html\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;color:rgb(43, 74, 66);font-family:'PT Sans Narrow', sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial\"><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;margin:0px;font-family:'PT Sans Narrow', sans-serif;font-style:normal;font-size:16px;line-height:1.45em\"><span style=\"font-family:'PT Sans Narrow', sans-serif\">Better rock tossing through magic! You create three Perfect Stones as the following <strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">one-handed thrown</strong> weapon - It is <strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">limited (3)</strong></span></p><table style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;width:642px;border-collapse:collapse;background:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);border-top:1px solid var(--color-border-light-tertiary);border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-border-light-tertiary);margin:0.5em 0px\"><tbody><tr style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\"><td style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;border:1px solid rgb(226, 232, 240);padding:0.25em 0px 0.25em 2px;text-align:left\"><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;margin:0px;font-family:'PT Sans Narrow', sans-serif;font-style:normal;font-size:16px;line-height:1.45em\"><span style=\"font-family:'PT Sans Narrow', sans-serif\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">Perfect Stones</strong></span></p></td><td style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;border:1px solid rgb(226, 232, 240);padding:0.25em 0px;text-align:left\"><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;margin:0px;font-family:'PT Sans Narrow', sans-serif;font-style:normal;font-size:16px;line-height:1.45em\"><span style=\"font-family:'PT Sans Narrow', sans-serif\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">【MIG + DEX】 or 【INS + WLP】</strong></span></p></td><td style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;border:1px solid rgb(226, 232, 240);padding:0.25em 0px;text-align:left\"><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;margin:0px;font-family:'PT Sans Narrow', sans-serif;font-style:normal;font-size:16px;line-height:1.45em;text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-family:'PT Sans Narrow', sans-serif\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">【HR + 10】Earth</strong></span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;margin:0px;font-family:'PT Sans Narrow', sans-serif;font-style:normal;font-size:16px;line-height:1.45em;color:rgb(43, 74, 66);font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start\"><span style=\"font-family:'PT Sans Narrow', sans-serif\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">Opportunity:</strong> Each target hit suffers <strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">@EFFECT[dazed]</strong>.</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;margin:10px 0px 0px;font-family:'PT Sans Narrow', sans-serif;font-style:normal;font-size:16px;line-height:1.45em;color:rgb(43, 74, 66);font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start\"><span style=\"font-family:'PT Sans Narrow', sans-serif\">If you have a free hand slot as you cast this spell, you may equip the Perfect Stones to it and make a <strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">free attack</strong> with one as part of the same action. When you’ve attacked with your third Perfect Stone, the effects of the spell end.</span></p><hr /><p><strong>@UUID[Item.Wo9LDqTbd4jGLsi6]{Perfect Stones} @LOSS[10 mp] </strong></p><p></p>",
